title: List of Primera División de Nicaragua seasons
text: The <a href="Primera%20Divisi%C3%B3n%20de%20Nicaragua">Primera División de Nicaragua</a> is the top division of <a href="Association%20football">football</a> in <a href="Nicaragua">Nicaragua</a>. This list shows the champions and movements in and out of the Primera División for each season since its foundation in 1933.
